<br>
My gut tells me any spell a druid casts should be clicked off immediately...and I'll ask the rangers for a sow.../chuckle <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uvilephire.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vilephire</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 74<br> <font color=#333333>(7/4/02 8:28:28 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=391.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Which raid buffs do you prefer?</span><hr size=1> I use the following raid buffs: Blessing of Aegolism, Khura's Focusing, Brell's Mountainous Barrier, Transon's Phantasmal Protection, Talisman of the Brute, Kodiak's Endless Intellect, Regrowth of the Grove, and whatever resistance buffs are needed for the particular encounter.<br>
<br>
Its more convenient for me to use this combination. We have our buffs done with MGB, and that is the extent of the majority of the buffing. I prefer this to having a Druid do PotG, then asking a Cleric to cast Symbol of Marzin or Marzin's Mark, then getting an AC buff (which isn't a concern of mine anyway.) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uknorotpumaslayer.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Knorot Pumaslayer</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mistress of The Elements</span><br>  Posts: 609<br> <font color=#333333>(7/4/02 8:31:01 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=391.topic&index=2>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Which raid buffs do you prefer?</span><hr size=1> I usually like to get:<br>
